comment: The internship at InnovateTech was an amazing experience. The team was supportive and I learned a ton about real-world AI applications.
Great course content, but the pace of the last module was a bit too fast. More examples would have been helpful.
The project was interesting, but mentorship was lacking. It was often hard to get guidance from my assigned mentor.
Excellent course! The instructor explained complex topics clearly and the projects were very practical.
